  <summary date="2022-05-03T17:53:34Z" status="Introduced in House">Pretrial Release Reporting Act

This bill requires the Bureau of Justice Statistics to submit a report to Congress on individuals who are granted bail or pretrial release from state courts and are charged with violent felony offenses (e.g., murder or rape).</summary>
